Below is a blog entry written by The Hebrew University of Jersusalem&#8217;s <a href="https://www.coursera.org/instructor/~284" target="_blank">Dr. Yuval Noah Harari</a> about his course <a href="https://www.coursera.org/course/humankind?utm_source=blog" target="_blank">A Brief History of Humankind</a>; started this week, August 10th. </i>
